# Week 5 Task 3 — YOLO Model Training

## Objective
Training a custom YOLO object detection model using a bottle detection dataset.

## Training Command

```bash
yolo detect train data=dataset/dataset.yaml model=yolo11n.pt epochs=100 imgsz=384
```

## Work Completed
- Used pretrained YOLO weights
- Trained model on custom bottle dataset
- Monitored training and validation loss
- Generated optimized model weights

## Training Results
- Precision: ~1.0
- Recall: ~0.999
- mAP50: ~0.995

## Output Files
- best.pt
- results.png
- confusion_matrix.png

## Tools Used
- Ultralytics YOLO
- FFmpeg
- Label Studio

## Outcome
Successfully trained a custom object detection model capable of detecting bottles in images.
